headline: NW Natural Names Kyra Patterson Chief People Officer
summary: PORTLAND, Ore., September 15, 2025--Northwest Natural Holding Company (NYSE:NWN) (NW Natural Holdings) has hired Kyra Patterson as its Chief People Officer, effective September 8, 2025.
